- `preferred_certifications` — English-normalized names. Empty array if none.
- `preferred_years_additional` — integer "extra" years beyond `years_experience_min` (e.g. requirements say 5+, preferred says 7+ → `preferred_years_additional = 2`). `null` if not distinct from requirements.

